<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;

 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>SqlSession</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>包含了执行</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>SQL</span><span

     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>JDBC</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>中的</span><span

     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>。</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>SqlSession</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>是应用程序与持久存储层之间执行交互操作的一个单线程对象，也是</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>MyBatis</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>执行持久化操作的关键对象</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>

     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>SqlSession</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>对象继承自</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US>Closeable</span><span

  <td style='border-style:solid;border-color:#A3A3A3;border-width:1pt;
  vertical-align:top;width:4.9611in;padding:2.0pt 3.0pt 2.0pt 3.0pt'>
  <p style='font-size:11.5pt'><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>关闭</span><span
  style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'>SqlSession</span><span style='font-family:
  "Microsoft YaHei UI"'>对象</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
  <td style='border-style:solid;border-color:#A3A3A3;border-width:1pt;
  background-color:#E7E6E6;vertical-align:top;width:1.6986in;padding:2.0pt 3.0pt 2.0pt 3.0pt'>
  <p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:11.5pt'><span
  lang=zh-CN>clearCache</span><span lang=en-US>()</span></p>
  </td>
  <td style='border-style:solid;border-color:#A3A3A3;border-width:1pt;
  background-color:#E7E6E6;vertical-align:top;width:5.0305in;padding:2.0pt 3.0pt 2.0pt 3.0pt'>
  <p style='font-size:11.5pt'><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>用于清空一级缓存（即会话缓存），即清空当前</span><span
  style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'> SqlSession </span><span
  style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>中缓存的所有数据。这样，下次该</span><span
  style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'> SqlSession </span><span
  style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>执行相同的</span><span style='font-family:
  "Comic Sans MS"'> SQL </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>语句时，就会重新发起</span><span
  style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'> SQL </span><span style='font-family:
  "Microsoft YaHei UI"'>查询，获取最新的数据。</span></p>
  <p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:11.5pt'>&nbsp;</p>
  <p style='font-size:11.5pt'><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>需要注意的是，</span><span
  style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'>clearCache() </span><span
  style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>方法只会清空当前</span><span
  style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'> SqlSession </span><span
  style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>中的缓存数据，对于其他</span><span
  style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'> SqlSession </span><span
  style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>的缓存数据不受影响。同时，二级缓存（即全局缓存）也不会受到影响，即使清空了当前</span><span
  style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'> SqlSession </span><span
  style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>的缓存数据，其他</span><span
  style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'> SqlSession </span><span
  style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>若从二级缓存中获取到了同样的数据，则仍然会直接使用缓存中的数据，而不会重新发起</span><span
  style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'> SQL </span><span style='font-family:
  "Microsoft YaHei UI"'>查询。</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
  <td style='border-style:solid;border-color:#A3A3A3;border-width:1pt;
  vertical-align:top;width:1.6986in;padding:2.0pt 3.0pt 2.0pt 3.0pt'>
  <p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:11.5pt'><span
  lang=zh-CN>getConfiguration</span><span lang=en-US>()</span></p>
  </td>
  <td style='border-style:solid;border-color:#A3A3A3;border-width:1pt;
  vertical-align:top;width:4.9611in;padding:2.0pt 3.0pt 2.0pt 3.0pt'>
  <p style='font-size:11.5pt'><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>方法返回的是</span><span
  style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'> SqlSession </span><span
  style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>对象所对应的</span><span style='font-family:
  "Comic Sans MS"'> MyBatis </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>配置对象</span><span
  style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'> Configuration</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
  <td style='border-style:solid;border-color:#A3A3A3;border-width:1pt;
  background-color:#E7E6E6;vertical-align:top;width:1.6986in;padding:2.0pt 3.0pt 2.0pt 3.0pt'>
  <p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:11.5pt'><span
  lang=zh-CN>getMapper</span><span lang=en-US>()</span></p>
  </td>
  <td style='border-style:solid;border-color:#A3A3A3;border-width:1pt;
  background-color:#E7E6E6;vertical-align:top;width:5.0305in;padding:2.0pt 3.0pt 2.0pt 3.0pt'>
  <p style='font-size:11.5pt'><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>返回</span><span
  style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'>mapper</span><span style='font-family:
  "Microsoft YaHei UI"'>接口的代理对象，该对象关联了</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'>SqlSession</span><span
  style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>对象，开发者可以通过该对象直接调用方法操作数据库，参数</span><span
  style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'>type</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>是</span><span
  style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'>Mapper</span><span style='font-family:
  "Microsoft YaHei UI"'>的接口类型。</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'>Mybatis</span><span
  style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>官方手册建议通过</span><span
  style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'>mapper</span><span style='font-family:
  "Microsoft YaHei UI"'>对象访问</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'>MyBatis</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
  <td style='border-style:solid;border-color:#A3A3A3;border-width:1pt;
  vertical-align:top;width:1.6986in;padding:2.0pt 3.0pt 2.0pt 3.0pt'>
  <p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:11.5pt'><span
  lang=zh-CN>getConnection</span><span lang=en-US>()</span></p>
  </td>
  <td style='border-style:solid;border-color:#A3A3A3;border-width:1pt;
  vertical-align:top;width:4.9611in;padding:2.0pt 3.0pt 2.0pt 3.0pt'>
  <p style='font-size:11.5pt'><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>获得</span><span
  style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'>JDBC</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>的数据库连接对象</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
</table>

</div>

<p style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;
color:#70AD47'><span style='font-weight:bold'>示例</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'><span lang=zh-CN>public class </span><span lang=en-US>User</span><span
lang=zh-CN>Test {</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt;color:#ED7D31'>@Test</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'><span lang=zh-CN>public void find</span><span lang=en-US>UserById</span><span
lang=zh-CN>Test() {</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-size:12.0pt;color:#70AD47'><span
style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'>// </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>获取</span><span
style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'> SqlSessionFactory </span><span
style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>对象</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>SqlSessionFactory sqlSessionFactory =
MyBatisUtils.getSqlSessionFactory();</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-size:12.0pt;color:#70AD47'><span
style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'>// </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>获取</span><span
style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'> SqlSession </span><span style='font-family:
"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>对象</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>SqlSession sqlSession = sqlSessionFactory.openSession();</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>try {</p>

<p style='margin-left:1.125in;font-size:12.0pt;color:#70AD47'><span
style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'>// </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>执行</span><span
style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'> SQL </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>查询，返回单一结果</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:1.125in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
font-size:12.0pt'>User user = sqlSession.selectOne(<span style='color:#70AD47'>&quot;com.example.mapper.UserMapper.selectUserById&quot;</span>,
1);</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:1.125in;font-size:12.0pt;color:#70AD47'><span
style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'>// </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>输出结果</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:1.125in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
font-size:12.0pt'>System.out.println(user);</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:1.125in;font-size:12.0pt;color:#70AD47'><span
style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'>// </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>提交事务</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:1.125in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
font-size:12.0pt'>sqlSession.commit();</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>} catch (Exception e) {</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-size:12.0pt'><span
style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>    </span></span><span
style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";color:#70AD47'>// </span><span
style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";color:#70AD47'>发生异常时回滚事务</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>    </span>sqlSession.rollback();</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>    </span>e.printStackTrace();</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>} finally {</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-size:12.0pt'><span
style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>    </span></span><span
style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";color:#70AD47'>// </span><span
style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";color:#70AD47'>关闭</span><span
style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";color:#70AD47'> SqlSession</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>    </span>sqlSession.close();</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>}</p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt' lang=en-US>}</p>

<p style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'><span
style='font-weight:bold'>注</span></p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>SqlSession </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>的实例不是线程安全的，因此是不能被共享的，所以它的最佳的作用域是请求或方法作用域。绝对不能将</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> SqlSession </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>实例的引用放在一个类的静态域，甚至一个类的实例变量也不行。也不能将</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> SqlSession </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>实例的引用放在任何类型的托管作用域中</span></li>
</ul>
